        <h1 data-i18n="heroTitle">The WCS you<br><span class="lime">actually control.</span></h1>
        <p class="lead" data-i18n="heroLead">
          openWCS orchestrates your automation — conveyors, ASRS, AMRs, AutoStore — and the
          real-time flow of goods, sitting between your WMS/ERP and the machines. Open,
          vendor-neutral, and yours to change.
        </p>
